{"tid":1786573,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"劉曉明冀澳門作為明燈照亮香港前進的道路","createTime":"2019-12-17T08:40:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T11:54:29.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"46af11e23637e767983dda19a9ae250601088943","tid":1786573,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T08:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1498141_1_20191217162652.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1498141_1_20191217162652.jpg&h=1728c4b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國駐英大使劉曉明在倫敦出席慶祝澳門回歸20周年活動，讚揚澳門取得舉世矚目的發展成就，向世界展現一國兩制、澳人治澳、高度自治的成功實踐，但同時表明不得不對近期香港事態表示痛心。<br />\n<br />\n劉曉明批評，國際上一些勢力不願見到中國順利發展，不願見到香港的一國兩制成功實施，希望澳門作為捍衛不干涉內政原則的明燈，照亮香港前進的道路，讓各界看清外來干涉的危害性，共同反對及抵制外來干涉，推動香港早日止暴制亂、恢復秩序，重回繁榮穩定的軌道。<br />\n<br />\n劉曉明相信，澳門與香港，一個東方「海上花園」，一個「東方之珠」，一定能夠再次比翼雙飛，共同續寫一國兩制成功實踐的新篇章。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1498141-20191217.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1498141-20191217.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0jk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=d0c2b674\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1498141-20191217.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c03be902\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1498141-20191217.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"ea98ec3c094dbbce08b29fbf44a2ad87caf2e46c","tid":1786573,"uid":15605,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T08:45:13.000Z","msg":"澳門係燈"},{"pid":"55d04532b4fa9a0f087f8edc92232430359edf33","tid":1786573,"uid":133522,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T08:45:30.000Z","msg":"我要左髀同埋右翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5322cef6512ed73d359109b4f70ea5045873a21d","tid":1786573,"uid":61235,"like":7,